cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "jami-pandoc: A reproducible Pandoc/Docker authoring environment for medical-informatics abstracts"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible, content/style-separated authoring environment that generates
  template-compliant Microsoft Word (.docx) conference abstracts from Markdown
  using Pandoc inside Docker, with deterministic builds, native SVG embedding,
  OOXML text boxes, and color-highlighted diffs for revision.
type: software
authors:
